      </div>

      <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:32px;">
        <p class="copy" style="color:var(--text-dim); max-width:52ch; margin:0 0 12px;">
          More speakers will be announced as confirmations land. If you are interested in
          contributing as a speaker or social science presenter, reach out directly.
        </p>
        <a class="btn-link-v3" href="mailto:oxford@llmsforsocialscience.net">
          Get in touch <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
